            "textpurpose":"Didactics",
            "textentryhtml":"Round 3.8 cm. diam with .3 cm. border containing a band of 5-point stars (at bottom edge, up to crenellation of building);.  Mao with red collar tab = in plain red circle in top ½ ; bkgd outside of this = red, +fine starburst. Building (Tian’anmen) + gate/wall below with furling flags in bkgd.  Inscription on red banner the folds of which reach outside edge of badge: “为人民立折功”. \r\nBack: small indentation, pin/clasp at top; Inscription below: “下川上山知识青年”.  Below this in smaller script = “北京”.\r\n",
